• LLaMA, Mistral, Qwen, YandexGPT; Ollama, vLLM, HuggingFace;

• Qdrant, Milvus, FAISS, эмбеддинги (E5, MiniLM), rerank;

• Python 3.10+, FastAPI, asyncio, SQLAlchemy;

• PostgreSQL, Oracle, ClickHouse.

